UNITED STATES of America, Plaintiff—Appellee, v. Coy Ray PHELPS, Defendant—Appellant. No. 02-10044. D.C. No. CR-85-00899-MHP. United States Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Submitted March 13, 2003.* Decided March 17, 2003.

Before GOODWIN, TASHIMA, and WARDLAW, Circuit Judges.

This panel unanimously finds this case suitable for decision without oral argument. See Fed. R.App. P. 34(a)(2).

ORDER **

This appeal is ordered dismissed as moot in light of United States v. Phelps, 283 F.3d 1176 (9th Cir.2002).

This disposition is not appropriate for publication and may not be cited to or by the courts of this circuit except as provided by Ninth Circuit Rule 36-3.
